{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Peacebringer takes the addictive auto-attacking gameplay of Vampire Survivors to the next level by introducing a party system. Build and control a team of heroes, each with their own unique abilities and attack patterns, as they battle against endless waves of corrupted beings. Master positioning and party composition to survive in a world being consumed by a twisted vision of peace.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STRATEGIC PARTY BUILDING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/peacebringer-gif-characters-3.gif?t=1739116205\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from 9 distinctive heroes, each with their own abilities and compelling backstories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your ideal party composition as you unlock new characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mix and match abilities like the Ranger's deadly bow skills, the Sorceress's chain lightning, or the Knight's defensive prowess</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MASTER THE CHAOS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/peacebringer-gif-combat.gif?t=1739116205\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Navigate through waves of corrupted beings in intense, action-packed battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Level up your heroes by collecting soul gems from fallen enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade abilities or choose powerful boons to enhance your entire party</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase permanent powerups using collected gold to strengthen your heroes</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE A DYING WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/gif-biomes.gif?t=1739116205\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Journey through 13 unique biomes, from the Whispering Pines to the nightmarish Obsidian Caldera</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle across 39 distinct stages, each with increasing challenges and dangers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new areas as you progress, revealing more of the corrupted landscape</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face a diverse array of enemies, from mischievous imps to terrifying dragons</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739116205","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/page.bg.jpg?t=1739116205","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/1fa5cdcde031d0066133350e152fffed48353ec3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739116205","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/1fa5cdcde031d0066133350e152fffed48353ec3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739116205","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"This game contains cartoon blood during combat."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Peacebringer takes the addictive auto-attacking gameplay of Vampire Survivors to the next level by introducing a party system. Build and control a team of heroes, each with their own unique abilities and attack patterns, as they battle against endless waves of corrupted beings. Master positioning and party composition to survive in a world being consumed by a twisted vision of peace.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STRATEGIC PARTY BUILDING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/peacebringer-gif-characters-3.gif?t=1739116205\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from 9 distincti